

=Bio=

"Bruno Carballa Smichowski is an economist and PhD candidate at Paris XIII University under Benjamin Coriat’s supervision. He has been working on competition-related issues in the so-called sharing economy, [[Data Commons]] and commons in general in the past 2 years."

